## 5. 데이터베이스

### diary 테이블

| 컬럼 | 타입 | 설명 |
|------|------|------|
| `id` | INTEGER PK | 자동증가 |
| `date` | TEXT UNIQUE | `"2026-02-24"` |
| `content` | TEXT | 최대 3줄 |
| `mood` | TEXT | `"HAPPY"` 등 |

### 핵심 쿼리

```sql
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO diary (date, content, mood) VALUES (?, ?, ?);
SELECT * FROM diary WHERE date = ?;
SELECT * FROM diary WHERE date LIKE '2026-02%';
SELECT mood, COUNT(*) as count FROM diary WHERE date LIKE '2026-02%' GROUP BY mood;
```

